# {{LABEL}} — Workbench Pipeline

Tracks every Jira epic in scope, every PRD under each epic, and the full chain of downstream artifacts and fix_plan execution.

**Update this file at the end of every session.** Read it at the start of every session.

---

## Pipeline key

| Symbol | Meaning |
|--------|---------|
| ✓ | Complete |
| ~ | In progress / in review |
| — | Not started |
| ✗ | Blocked |

